50|$|The Riemann-Lebesgue lemma {{can be used}} {{to prove}} the {{validity}} of asymptotic approximations for integrals. Rigorous treatments of the <b>method</b> <b>of</b> <b>steepest</b> <b>descent</b> and the method of stationary phase, amongst others, are based on the Riemann-Lebesgue lemma.|$|E
